El cumpleaños de este viejo no es tan importante.

00:10:22.640 --> 00:10:23.650
¿Y Jae Won?

00:10:23.650 --> 00:10:25.730
Jae Won está...

00:10:27.450 --> 00:10:29.210
aquí mismo.

00:10:29.210 --> 00:10:30.170
Hola.

00:10:30.170 --> 00:10:34.650
